[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/alacritty/alacritty/issues/comments/485022744","html_url":"https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty/issues/2337#issuecomment-485022744","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/alacritty/alacritty/issues/2337","id":485022744,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDQ4NTAyMjc0NA==","user":{"login":"chrisduerr","id":8886672,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjg4ODY2NzI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8886672?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr","html_url":"https://github.com/chrisduerr","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2019-04-19T21:50:21Z","updated_at":"2019-04-19T21:50:21Z","body":"I'm unsure how exactly iTerm has fixed this since their gitlab/github mixture isn't exactly simple to follow, but I've got a patch for the Info.plist file which might help:\r\n\r\n```diff\r\ndiff --git a/extra/osx/Alacritty.app/Contents/Info.plist b/extra/osx/Alacritty.app/Contents/Info.plist\r\nindex da1aea7..08b7eec 100644\r\n--- a/extra/osx/Alacritty.app/Contents/Info.plist\r\n+++ b/extra/osx/Alacritty.app/Contents/Info.plist\r\n@@ -52,5 +52,7 @@\r\n     <string>An application in Alacritty would like to access your microphone.</string>\r\n     <key>NSRemindersUsageDescription</key>\r\n     <string>An application in Alacritty would like to access your reminders.</string>\r\n+    <key>NSSystemAdministrationUsageDescription</key>\r\n+\t<string>The operation being performed by a program in Alacritty requires elevated permission.</string>\r\n </dict>\r\n </plist>\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis seems to be the only Info.plist thing even remotely close to requesting elevated storage access, so hopefully that does it. I believe iTerm originally did this through source code, but they've removed that and go through the Info.plist now.","author_association":"MEMBER","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/alacritty/alacritty/issues/comments/485022744/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"chrisduerr","id":8886672,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjg4ODY2NzI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8886672?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr","html_url":"https://github.com/chrisduerr","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/chrisduerr/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"id":2289070905,"node_id":"MDEyOkxhYmVsZWRFdmVudDIyODkwNzA5MDU=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/alacritty/alacritty/issues/events/2289070905","actor":{"login":"chrisduerr","id":8886672,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjg4ODY2NzI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubuse